<h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<div class="language-typescript ext-ts line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-typescript"><code><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token keyword">type</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>Except<span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> <span class="token string">'type-fest'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

