<li><code v-pre>RecordDeep</code>- See <a href="https://github.com/sindresorhus/type-fest/blob/main/source/schema.d.ts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code v-pre>Schema</code><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
<li><code v-pre>Mutable</code>- See <a href="https://github.com/sindresorhus/type-fest/blob/main/source/writable.d.ts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code v-pre>Writable</code><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="tips" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#tips" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Tips</h2>
<h3 id="extending-existing-types" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#extending-existing-types" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Extending existing types</h3>
<ul>
<li>
